Localization.Name: Gladius Dunlevy Model
Localization.Description: This exquisitely detailed Gladius model honors the light fighter that's been protecting the UEE for centuries. Soaring above a stand featuring the UEE logo and ship's name, the Dunlevy variant of the Gladius was crafted to honor Captain Alexandra Dunlevy, who shaped the course of the Navy's elite Squadron 42.

Localization.Name: Carrack Miniature
Localization.Description: Takuetsu has finally set their expert eye on the Carrack. Using schematics supplied by Anvil Aerospace, this intricately detailed miniature captures the look and spirit of the beloved exploration ship that's spawned countless adventures across the empire.
